name: Mr. Dice
description: This is Mr. Dice. It's our original set. We are proud of it and think you will be too.

name: Mrs. Dice
description: Nearly the same as our Mr. Dice, but it looks different, and is cheaper.

name: D20
description: This is a D20. Please buy it from us.

name: D12
description: It's not a D20. It's not a D10. It's a D12. For D12 things, we presume.

name: D10

name: D8

name: D6
description: Have you ever considered getting a life? No? Cool. Neither have I.

name: D4
description: This one is triangle shaped. Illuminati? Pyramids? Aliens? Yes. That.

name: Broken Dice :(
description: Oh no! Our dice! It's broken!

name: Software Engineer's Tears
description: Plentiful. Unshowered. Salty. Foodsafe. Somehow green in color.
